PDB is VERY important exactly in the node drain / upgrade situation you described. â€œDuring voluntary disruptions (like drain, upgrade), how many pods are allowed to go down at a time.â€

It protects your application from downtime.

apiVersion: policy/v1
kind: PodDisruptionBudget
metadata:
  name: app-pdb
  namespace: default
spec:
  minAvailable: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: my-app
